Package com.microsoft.azure.cognitiveservices.faceapi

This package contains the classes for FaceAPI. An API for face detection, verification, and identification.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccessoryItem
    Accessory item and corresponding confidence level.
    APIError
    Error information returned by the API.
    BlurProperties
    Properties describing any presence of blur within the image.
    ColorProperty
    Hair color and associated confidence.
    CreateFaceListRequest
    Request to create a face list.
    CreatePersonGroupRequest
    Request to create a person group.
    CreatePersonRequest
    Request to create a person object.
    EmotionProperties
    Properties describing facial emotion in form of confidence ranging from 0 to 1.
    Error
    Error body.
    ExposureProperties
    Properties describing exposure level of the image.
    FaceAttributes
    Face Attributes.
    FaceLandmarks
    A collection of 27-point face landmarks pointing to the important positions of face components.
    FaceRectangle
    A rectangle within which a face can be found.
    FacialHairProperties
    Properties describing facial hair attributes.
    FindSimilarRequest
    Request body for find similar operation.
    GroupRequest
    Request body for group request.
    HairProperties
    Properties describing hair attributes.
    HeadPoseProperties
    Properties indicating head pose of the face.
    IdentifyRequest
    Request body for identify face operation.
    IdentifyResultCandidate
    All possible faces that may qualify.
    ImageUrl
    The ImageUrl model.
    MakeupProperties
    Properties describing present makeups on a given face.
    NoiseProperties
    Properties describing noise level of the image.
    OcclusionProperties
    Properties describing occulusions on a given face.
    Position
    Coordinates within an image.
    UpdatePersonFaceDataRequest

    VerifyPersonGroupRequest

    Request body for verify operation.
